sequenceDiagram
    actor Guard as Security Guard
    participant UI as JavaFX Monitoring Screen
    participant Service as MonitoringService
    participant DAO as DeviceLogDAO / DeviceDAO
    participant DB as Relational Database
    participant Audit as AuditService

    Guard->>UI: Search student ID or serial number
    UI->>Service: findDeviceForIngress(criteria)
    Service->>DAO: query device and latest log
    DAO->>DB: SELECT device/log status
    DB-->>DAO: Device and status data
    DAO-->>Service: Device record
    Service-->>UI: Display verification details
    Guard->>UI: Confirm visual verification and log ingress
    UI->>Service: logIngress(deviceId, currentUser)
    Service->>Service: Validate approved/eligible, active, outside
    Service->>DAO: Insert ingress log and set campus_status Inside
    DAO->>DB: INSERT device_logs; UPDATE devices
    Service->>Audit: record ingress event
    Service-->>UI: Success or validation error

